💎💎💎

Claudius AE Assarius 🦒 Emperor from 41-54 AD. First Roman emperor to be born outside of Rome. Predecessor: Caligula (37-41 AD). Successor: Nero (54-68 AD). This is a beautiful example of his coinage! Large portrait of Claudius I on the obverse & a full image of Constantiae on the back. Not for sale. #headyart #ancientart #romanempire #ancientcoins #ancientcoin
